959	Neonatal Jaundice (variante 958)	Otra	Phototherapy, exchange transfusion (in severe cases), monitoring of bilirubin levels, addressing underlying causes (e.g., breastfeeding)	t	Enfermedad registrada: Neonatal Jaundice
960	Conjunctivitis due to Allergy (variante 959)	Otra	Allergen avoidance, antihistamine eye drops, cold compresses, lubricating eye drops	f	Enfermedad registrada: Conjunctivitis due to Allergy
961	Drug Abuse (Barbiturates) (variante 960)	Otra	Medical detoxification, supportive care, counseling, rehabilitation programs	f	Enfermedad registrada: Drug Abuse (Barbiturates)
963	Cryptorchidism (variante 962)	Otra	Observation and monitoring (in cases of mild or transient cryptorchidism), hormone therapy (to stimulate testicular descent), surgical intervention (orchiopexy) to reposition the testicle(s) into the scrotum, if necessary, performed around the age of 6 to 12 months, open or laparoscopic surgery (in cases of high or persistent cryptorchidism), testicular prostheses (in cases of absent or non-functional testicles), regular follow-up visits with a urologist or pediatric surgeon	t	Enfermedad registrada: Cryptorchidism
964	Cornea Infection (variante 963)	Otra	Antibiotic or antifungal eye drops, oral medications, supportive care, possible corneal transplant (in severe cases)	t	Enfermedad registrada: Cornea Infection
965	infection urinary tract (variante 964)	Otra	\N	f	Enfermedad registrada: infection urinary tract
966	Ethylene glycol poisoning-1 (variante 965)	Otra	Supportive Measures, Gastric Decontamination, Antidote Administration, Hemodialysis	f	Enfermedad registrada: Ethylene glycol poisoning-1
967	Lymphoma (variante 966)	Otra	Chemotherapy, radiation therapy, immunotherapy, targeted therapy	t	Enfermedad registrada: Lymphoma
968	Migraine (variante 967)	Otra	pain relief medication, rest, cold compress	t	Enfermedad registrada: Migraine
969	ulcer peptic (variante 968)	Otra	\N	f	Enfermedad registrada: ulcer peptic
970	Hirschsprung Disease (variante 969)	Otra	Surgery to remove the affected part of the colon (pull-through procedure)	t	Enfermedad registrada: Hirschsprung Disease
971	Peritonsillar Abscess (variante 970)	Otra	Antibiotics to treat infection, drainage of the abscess (needle aspiration or incision and drainage), pain relievers, warm saltwater gargles, rest, fluids, surgical removal of the tonsils (in chronic or recurrent cases)	t	Enfermedad registrada: Peritonsillar Abscess
972	Hemorrhoids (variante 971)	Otra	Increasing fiber intake, staying hydrated, avoiding straining during bowel movements, warm sitz baths, topical creams or ointments, over-the-counter pain relievers (after consulting with a healthcare provider)	f	Enfermedad registrada: Hemorrhoids
973	Liver Disease (variante 972)	Otra	\N	f	Enfermedad registrada: Liver Disease
974	coronary heart disease (variante 973)	Otra	\N	f	Enfermedad registrada: coronary heart disease
975	biliary calculus (variante 974)	Otra	\N	f	Enfermedad registrada: biliary calculus
976	Juvenile Rheumatoid Arthritis (variante 975)	Otra	Medications (NSAIDs, DMARDs), physical therapy, occupational therapy, exercise, assistive devices	t	Enfermedad registrada: Juvenile Rheumatoid Arthritis
977	Benzodiazepine Use Disorder (variante 976)	Otra	Gradual tapering off benzodiazepines under medical supervision, counseling or therapy (such as cognitive-behavioral therapy), support groups, addressing underlying psychological or social factors, lifestyle changes, addressing co-occurring mental health conditions, harm reduction strategies, ongoing monitoring and support	t	Enfermedad registrada: Benzodiazepine Use Disorder
978	Coagulation (Bleeding) Disorder (variante 977)	Otra	Blood transfusions, clotting factor replacement therapy, medications to stimulate clotting, lifestyle modifications, surgery (in some cases)	t	Enfermedad registrada: Coagulation (Bleeding) Disorder
979	Syndrome of Inappropriate Secretion of ADH (SIADH) (variante 978)	Otra	Treating underlying cause, fluid restriction, medications to suppress ADH (vasopressin) secretion, addressing electrolyte imbalance	t	Enfermedad registrada: Syndrome of Inappropriate Secretion of ADH (SIADH)
980	Marijuana Abuse (variante 979)	Otra	Behavioral therapy, counseling, support groups, medication, detoxification	t	Enfermedad registrada: Marijuana Abuse
981	Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD) (variante 980)	Otra	Behavioral therapy, parent training programs, medication (such as stimulants or non-stimulants), individualized education plans (IEPs) for academic support, accommodations and modifications in school, psychoeducation, counseling	t	Enfermedad registrada: Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD)
982	Abscess of Nose (variante 981)	Otra	Antibiotics, warm compresses, surgical drainage (in severe cases)	f	Enfermedad registrada: Abscess of Nose
983	Parasitic Infections (variante 982)	Otra	Prescription medications (topical or oral antiparasitic agents), washing clothes and bedding in hot water	t	Enfermedad registrada: Parasitic Infections
984	Dislocation of the Patella (variante 983)	Otra	Manual reduction, immobilization, physical therapy	t	Enfermedad registrada: Dislocation of the Patella
985	Lice (variante 984)	Otra	Over-the-counter or prescription medications specifically designed to kill lice (such as pediculicides), manual removal of lice and nits using a fine-toothed comb, washing and drying of infested clothing and bedding at high temperatures, vacuuming of upholstery and household surfaces, disinfection of personal items that cannot be washed or dried, avoiding direct head-to-head contact with infested individuals, education and prevention strategies	t	Enfermedad registrada: Lice
986	Fat Embolism (variante 985)	Otra	Supportive care (oxygen therapy, fluid resuscitation), managing symptoms (pain medication, anticoagulants), treatment of underlying cause if possible	t	Enfermedad registrada: Fat Embolism
987	Transient ischemic attack (variante 986)	Otra	Antiplatelet medications, Carotid endarterectomy,  Anticoagulant medications, Lifestyle modifications	t	Enfermedad registrada: Transient ischemic attack
988	incontinence (variante 987)	Otra	\N	f	Enfermedad registrada: incontinence
989	Temporomandibular Joint Disorder (variante 988)	Otra	Self-care measures (rest, applying heat or cold, jaw exercises), pain medications, physical therapy, oral splints	t	Enfermedad registrada: Temporomandibular Joint Disorder
990	lymphoma (variante 989)	Otra	\N	f	Enfermedad registrada: lymphoma
991	Acute Bronchospasm (variante 990)	Otra	Bronchodilators (inhaled medications), corticosteroids, supplemental oxygen (if needed)	t	Enfermedad registrada: Acute Bronchospasm
992	Cranial Nerve Palsy (variante 991)	Otra	Treatment depends on the underlying cause and specific cranial nerve affected. It may include medications (such as corticosteroids or antiviral drugs), physical therapy, speech therapy, occupational therapy, eye exercises, surgery (in some cases), and management of any underlying conditions.	t	Enfermedad registrada: Cranial Nerve Palsy
993	Choledocholithiasis (variante 992)	Otra	Non-surgical treatment options: Medications to manage pain and discomfort, antibiotics	t	Enfermedad registrada: Choledocholithiasis
994	Endometrial Cancer (variante 993)	Otra	Surgery (hysterectomy), radiation therapy, chemotherapy, hormone therapy	t	Enfermedad registrada: Endometrial Cancer
995	hyperlipidemia (variante 994)	Otra	\N	f	Enfermedad registrada: hyperlipidemia
996	Aplastic Anemia (variante 995)	Otra	Blood transfusions, bone marrow-stimulating medications, immunosuppressive therapy, stem cell transplant (in severe cases), supportive care	t	Enfermedad registrada: Aplastic Anemia
997	Preeclampsia (variante 996)	Otra	Bed rest, blood pressure monitoring, frequent prenatal visits, medication (such as antihypertensive drugs), magnesium sulfate (for severe cases), delivery of the baby (in severe cases)	t	Enfermedad registrada: Preeclampsia
998	pericardial effusion body substance (variante 997)	Otra	\N	f	Enfermedad registrada: pericardial effusion body substance
999	infection (variante 998)	Otra	\N	f	Enfermedad registrada: infection
1000	Encephalitis (variante 999)	Otra	Hospitalization, antiviral medications (if caused by a viral infection), supportive care	t	Enfermedad registrada: Encephalitis
